{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_OSK_270.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Welcome. Why are you all here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Um... We were wondering how you were doing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "We're concerned about you after the Eternal Blossom incident the other day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hey!? Plachta, you could put it a little more gently."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oskar?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I was really shocked when I was told that plants lie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "All I wanted was to know more about plants. I wanted to get to know them, and be friends..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "But that was just my one-sided desire..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Oskar..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x1c,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "What are you talking about? That's normal."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "What!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Monika...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x1d,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "People are the same way, you know?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x1d,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Just because people can talk to each other doesn't mean everyone gets along all the time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x1e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Sometimes we fight, or lie. But that isn't a reason to hate every single person."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "That's..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "There's nothing to worry about."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "You want to be friends with those plants, right? You want to see the Eternal Blossom too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "What are you so worried about? You already know what you want to do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "First, you need to talk to them. Then you need to find out why that plant lied to you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Maybe you'll understand something when you do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Monika... Yeah, you're right. I was feeling too depressed about this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Thanks, Monika. I feel better now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "That's good. That gloomy look wasn't very fitting of you, Oskar."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Heh heh... On a related note, I have something to ask you all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "You want to go to the Forest of Fairies again, right? We already know."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Thanks."
        }
    ]
}